'''人类自愿灭绝运动'''（{{lang-en|Voluntary Human Extinction Movement}}，简称{{lang|en|VHEMT}}{{#tag:ref|发音为{{lang|en|vehement}}，直译是“激越”的意思<ref name="npr">{{cite news | last = Pesca | first = Mike | title = All Choked Up | url = http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=5401422 | accessdate = 2015-02-12 | newspaper = NPR | date = 2006-05-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141025042327/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=5401422 | archivedate = 2014-10-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>；据创始人乐斯·奈特所言，这是个“激越”组织<ref name="te">{{cite news | title = Sui genocide | archivedate = 2013-10-20 | url = http://www.economist.com/node/179963 | accessdate = 2015-02-12 | newspaper = The Economist | date = 1998-12-17 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131020133620/http://www.economist.com/node/179963 }}</ref>。|group="注"}}）是一场号召所有人放弃生育，逐步实现自愿性[[人类灭绝|人类灭绝]]的[[環保運動|环保运动]]。运动的支持者认为人类灭绝可以防止[[环境恶化|环境恶化]]，该组织称[[人口過多|人口過多]]存在多种危害，如物种灭绝、人类所需资源短缺等，减少人口就能显著减少人为因素造成的苦难。

奈特1991年创立人类自愿灭绝运动组织，他曾于20世纪70年代参与[[美国环境保护运动|美国环境保护运动]]，认为人类灭绝是解决地球[[生物圈|生物圈]]和人性面临问题的最佳途径。奈特还为组织发布新闻通讯并担任发言人。该团体主要依靠外部媒体传播信息，此外还有网站宣传，并在部分环境运动中发挥作用。许多评论人士将其视为无法接受的极端组织，但也有作家称赞人类自愿灭绝运动的视角。部分[[记者|记者]]和学者认为人类可以创造出可持续的生活方式，也能把人口减少到可持续水平。其他人则坚持认为无论这一种想法有多么优越，人类繁殖的本能都会防止人类在自愿情况下灭绝。

== 历史 ==
人类自愿灭绝运动组织由乐斯·奈特创办<ref name="te" /><ref name="ti" />，不过他本人对此否认，称自己不是创始人，只是为其命名<ref>{{cite web | title = Personal information about Les U. Knight | url = http://www.vhemt.org/les.htm | publisher = The Voluntary Human Extinction Movement | accessdate = 2015-02-12 | archivedate = 2013-10-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131022153115/http://www.vhemt.org/les.htm }}</ref>。他是位生活在[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特兰]]的中学代课教师<ref name="te"/>。奈特在大家庭中长大<ref name="sfc" />，在高校期间曾投身20世纪70年代的环境保护运动，认为地球所面临的大部分危机都是人口过多所致。得出这样的结论后，他加入[[人口零增长|人口零增长]]组织<ref name="te" />，并在25岁那年做了[[輸精管結紮術|輸精管結紮術]]<ref name="sfc">{{cite news | last = Dicum | first = Gregory | title = Maybe None | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-10-20 | url = http://www.sfgate.com/homeandgarden/article/GREEN-Maybe-None-Is-having-a-child-even-one-3236285.php | accessdate = 2013-10-19 | newspaper = San Francisco Chronicle | date = 2005-11-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131020073543/http://www.sfgate.com/homeandgarden/article/GREEN-Maybe-None-Is-having-a-child-even-one-3236285.php }}</ref>。之后他进一步认为，要解决地球环境问题，最好的办法就是让人类灭绝<ref name="te" />。他还相信，历史上一直都有人抱持同样理念<ref name="Ormrod">{{cite journal | last = Ormrod | first = James S. | title = 'Making room for the tigers and the polar bears': Biography, phantasy and ideology in the Voluntary Human Extinction Movement | journal = Psychoanalysis, Culture & Society | year = 2011 | volume = 16 | issue = 2 | doi = 10.1057/pcs.2009.30}}</ref>{{rp|142}}。

1991年，奈特开始发布人类自愿灭绝运动新闻通讯<ref name="te" />《这些退出的时代》<ref name="ti" />。在通讯中，他要求读者以不再繁殖来实现进一步的人类灭绝<ref name="te" />。他还出版漫画作品<ref name="ta">{{cite news |title=Sites answer 300 million questions |url=http://www.timesargus.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=/20061022/NEWS/610220322/1016/FEATURES07 |accessdate=2015-02-12 |newspaper=Barre Montpelier Times Argus |date=2006-10-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019235441/http://www.timesargus.com/apps/pbcs.dll/article?AID=%2F20061022%2FNEWS%2F610220322%2F1016%2FFEATURES07 |archivedate=2013-10-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，例如连环画《黑猩猩婴儿》就讲述了一位女性放弃生育，选择收养一只[[倭黑猩猩|倭黑猩猩]]的故事<ref name="ti">{{cite news | last = Jarvis | first = Stephen | title = Live long and die out: Stephen Jarvis encounters the Voluntary Human Extinction Movement | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/live-long-and-die-out-stephen-jarvis-encounters-the-voluntary-human-extinction-movement-1372200.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131214202942/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/live-long-and-die-out-stephen-jarvis-encounters-the-voluntary-human-extinction-movement-1372200.html | archivedate = 2013-12-14 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-02-12 | newspaper = The Independent | date = 1994-04-24 }}</ref>。1996年，奈特为人类自愿灭绝运动创办了网站<ref name="Ormrod" />{{rp|143}}，到2010年时已有11种语言版本<ref name="Weisman">{{cite book |last=Weisman |first=Alan |title=The World Without Us |year=2010 |publisher=HarperCollins |isbn=978-1-4434-0008-4}}</ref>{{rp|310}}。人类自愿灭绝运动的标识包括字母“{{lang|en|V}}”，代表“{{lang|en|voluntary}}”（意为“自愿”），还有反向的[[地球|地球]]（即南北方向倒转，南在上，北在下）<ref name="vhemtlogo">{{cite web | title = Symbolism of the logo for the Voluntary Human Extinction Movement | url = http://vhemt.org/logo.htm | publisher = Voluntary Human Extinction Movement | accessdate = 2015-02-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141217060340/http://www.vhemt.org/logo.htm | archivedate = 2014-12-17 }}</ref>，根据组织的说法，反向地球代表人类自愿灭绝运动的目标：对人类发展作出根本性转变，因为反向标志经常用于代表危难<ref name="vhemtlogo" />。

== 组织和推广 ==
人类自愿灭绝运动结构松散，没有正式、严谨的组织<ref name="Ormrod" />{{rp|142-143}}，连成员名单也没有汇编出来。[[威拉姆特大学|威拉姆特大学]]的丹尼尔·梅斯表示，1995年时该运动的邮寄名单中只有不到400名订阅者<ref name="te" />。6年后，[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞頻道]]报道称这个名单上只有230名订阅者<ref name="fox">{{cite news |title=Anti-People Group Pushes for Man's Extinction |url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/2001/07/29/anti-people-group-pushes-for-man-extinction/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130517032408/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2001/07/29/anti-people-group-pushes-for-man-extinction/ |archivedate=2013-05-17 |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2013-10-19 |newspaper=Foxnews.com |date=2011-07-29 }}</ref>。奈特称，认同他思想的人就是组织成员<ref name="te" />，这样的人有“数百万”之多<ref name="aboutvhemt">{{cite web |url=http://vhemt.org/aboutvhemt.htm |title=About The Movement — When and how did VHEMT start? |publisher=The Voluntary Human Extinction Movement |accessdate=2013-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728181647/http://www.vhemt.org/aboutvhemt.htm |archivedate=2013-07-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。从团体网站上的宣传来看，人类自愿灭绝运动的参与者都是“志愿者”、“支持者”或是“拿不定主意的人”，减少人类的出生率是这些人的共同意愿<ref name="Join">{{cite web |url=http://vhemt.org/join.htm |publisher=The Voluntary Human Extinction Movement |title=How to join VHEMT |accessdate=2013-10-19 |archivedate=2013-09-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929231608/http://www.vhemt.org/join.htm |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

奈特是人类自愿灭绝运动的发言人<ref name="te" />。他代表组织出席环境会议和活动，并在这些地方宣传有关人口增长的信息<ref name="Weisman" />{{rp|310}}。不过，人类自愿灭绝运动的信息主要还是通过外界媒体进行传播，而非活动和新闻通讯<ref name="Ormrod" />{{rp|143}}。人类自愿灭绝运动会销售钮扣和T恤衫<ref name="Ormrod" />{{rp|143}}，还有印着“感谢您不生孩子”的汽车保险杠贴纸<ref name="ti" />。

== 思想 ==
{{Quote box
 |quote  = 我们是唯一进化到会为了所有生命的利益而自愿灭绝的物种，并且这也是必要的。
 |source = 人类自愿灭绝运动网站<ref>{{cite web |title=SUCCESS |url=http://vhemt.org/success.htm#poss |work=Voluntary Human Extinction Movement Website |publisher=vhemt.org |quote=We're the only species evolved enough to consciously go extinct for the good of all life, or which needs to. |accessdate=2013-10-19 |archivedate=2013-07-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728180428/http://www.vhemt.org/success.htm#poss }}</ref>
